{"tid":53750,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺教會同健身黑店係一撚樣","createTime":"2016-12-25T02:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T15:08:17.000Z","uid":21830,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b57daff3038d7d962df458efbd4d27ace8f9e5ba","tid":53750,"uid":21830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:58:13.000Z","msg":"免費試玩，趁住你喺人哋主場不停sale鳩你<br />\n<br />\n不停鼓勵你帶埋個friend嚟一齊玩<br />\n<br />\n初期通常有一對一輔導，話你身體好差/心靈空虛要勤啲做training/返崇拜<br />\n<br />\n「平有平做，貴有貴做」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗到再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65c3f5e537d78cc85bd8e5dd928652bd172e0bb","tid":53750,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:59:46.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"6432ba568d5f27566939f136931a212d3db95e58","tid":53750,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:00:29.000Z","msg":"教會唔係識女用㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f626f9cc8568651f7bae83ee0b038f94b63ed00a","tid":53750,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:03:21.000Z","msg":"屌，班耶撚自己要信咪信飽佢囉，點解要迫人信洗鳩人腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79a386de2438cb028f036b9b6c2d5564892ea4c","tid":53750,"uid":45678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:05:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教會唔係識女用㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喺gym都可以既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e020650aa5d727d56c0e23c55a45f4234c87493f","tid":53750,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:05:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教會唔係識女用㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做牧師先爽<br />\n個個住大屋揸靚車<br />\n收會員十一奉獻又唔洗交稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51c66c8698c574ad1fd50267782d62a1a156724","tid":53750,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:08:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>教會唔係識女用㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喺gym都可以既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教會啲女純啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做gym都係想塑造好啲嘅身材吸引異性姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淫啲"},{"pid":"9ad24ba94f338d3c036cc7b9be430571b72a9180","tid":53750,"uid":15195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:11:29.000Z","msg":"講野去過一次教會<br />\n真係好戇鳩<br />\n一開始成班人圍威喂坐埋一齊好似傾計咁<br />\n之後個牧師就黎料<br />\n搵幾條撚樣上台講下自己啲所謂見證<br />\n之後就開始問<br />\n有冇人願意跟耶穌<br />\n有冇人願意跟我一齊信耶穌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n願意既話一齊企起身<br />\n跟住在場連埋自己啲fd(本身耶撚黎）<br />\n都企左起身得你自己一個坐係到<br />\n個fd都噓你叫你企起身<br />\n跟撚本成個傳銷咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n戇鳩 仲有成撚日去啲醫院搵啲就死既人叫佢地信耶穌<br />\n就可以上天堂 <br />\n好撚心你班撚樣啦<br />\n人地本身有其他信仰<br />\n你依加叫人中途出家信耶穌<br />\n啲人真係心軟點左頭<br />\n本身個個都當佢25<br />\n之後呢個都未必收啦<br />\n痴撚線<br />\n垃圾耶撚"},{"pid":"b111701b990dcbe14260ad93232b0f16caa5a179","tid":53750,"uid":50620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教會唔係識女用㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教會d女先唔好識<br />\n冇得啪唔再講，週街kiss同單獨共處一室都要避免<br />\n好火熱既除左星期六日你都預佢有幾日平日都返教會唔知整乜<br />\n<br />\n煩過閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293d588e4a39f3c9e788928f9d7c4214771d2d6a","tid":53750,"uid":21501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:13:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 健身黑店&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;教會"},{"pid":"55ffecd95267c9afc4d2870abd7a8b16367a4e50","tid":53750,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:14:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>教會唔係識女用㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教會d女先唔好識<br />\n冇得啪唔再講，週街kiss同單獨共處一室都要避免<br />\n好火熱既除左星期六日你都預佢有幾日平日都返教會唔知整乜<br />\n<br />\n煩過閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識個耶撚女<br />\n出名淫"},{"pid":"cf62f3f14e59e81c3845eec78e3576e542d31cad","tid":53750,"uid":14905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:24:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>教會唔係識女用㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喺gym都可以既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教會啲女純啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做gym都係想塑造好啲嘅身材吸引異性姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淫啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你以為 我識啲女返教會既都唔係處 反而真正純個啲全部冇返"},{"pid":"43393dac265e744bab19b3afe6fa1ed2ccd0e2fd","tid":53750,"uid":14905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:25:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講野去過一次教會<br />\n真係好戇鳩<br />\n一開始成班人圍威喂坐埋一齊好似傾計咁<br />\n之後個牧師就黎料<br />\n搵幾條撚樣上台講下自己啲所謂見證<br />\n之後就開始問<br />\n有冇人願意跟耶穌<br />\n有冇人願意跟我一齊信耶穌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n願意既話一齊企起身<br />\n跟住在場連埋自己啲fd(本身耶撚黎）<br />\n都企左起身得你自己一個坐係到<br />\n個fd都噓你叫你企起身<br />\n跟撚本成個傳銷咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n戇鳩 仲有成撚日去啲醫院搵啲就死既人叫佢地信耶穌<br />\n就可以上天堂 <br />\n好撚心你班撚樣啦<br />\n人地本身有其他信仰<br />\n你依加叫人中途出家信耶穌<br />\n啲人真係心軟點左頭<br />\n本身個個都當佢25<br />\n之後呢個都未必收啦<br />\n痴撚線<br />\n垃圾耶撚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用群眾壓力逼你企起身逼你信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e192fe96625b18118a82517332eefba2f94bbb9","tid":53750,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:26:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喺gym都可以既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教會啲女純啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做gym都係想塑造好啲嘅身材吸引異性姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淫啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你以為 我識啲女返教會既都唔係處 反而真正純個啲全部冇返</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sor囉 鳩估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309cf5e3017e84c5c542c5936004ea62952aa4ad","tid":53750,"uid":21830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:12:34.000Z","msg":"耶撚同健身撚都會拎年資嚟打飛機"},{"pid":"ca3a096c35a09da4d03d5a8706a8e27ec26b3244","tid":53750,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:07:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>教會唔係識女用㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教會d女先唔好識<br />\n冇得啪唔再講，週街kiss同單獨共處一室都要避免<br />\n好火熱既除左星期六日你都預佢有幾日平日都返教會唔知整乜<br />\n<br />\n煩過閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n祈完禱"},{"pid":"796c48fa5de5cd92aee01289e37eb832116a7089","tid":53750,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:08:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>教會唔係識女用㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教會d女先唔好識<br />\n冇得啪唔再講，週街kiss同單獨共處一室都要避免<br />\n好火熱既除左星期六日你都預佢有幾日平日都返教會唔知整乜<br />\n<br />\n煩過閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n祈完禱變處女,邊到搵"}]}